item.title: Samsung's new smartphones are now up for preorder — here's how to get a Galaxy Z Fold6 or Z Flip6
item.description: As of July 10, Samsung's new smartphones — the Galaxy Z Fold6 and Z Flip6 — are now up for preorder. Here's how to get your hands on one.

item.title: Samsung taps Sydney Sweeney and K-pop stars TXT for its Unpacked event
item.description: Sydney Sweeney attended Samsung Unpacked 2024 in Paris, and K-Pop group Tomorrow X Together and a digital magician made cameos.

item.title: Samsung gives your doodles the AI treatment with 'sketch-to-image'
item.description: At Samsung Unpacked 2024, the company announced AI updates including a new "sketch-to-image" feature on Galaxy products.
